data.description: PRICE REDUCED! SELLER MOTIVATED! Completely Remodeled 3bed/2bath Pool Home in the prestigious thought-out Bel Aire community. Make this gorgeous property your new home and relax around the pool in a hamaca. Significant upgrades done includes new roof, impact windows & doors, electrical, A/C, kitchen with high-end high efficiency S/S Appliances including wine cooler, upgraded bathrooms, California closets, luxurious porcelain tiles throughout, high-end washer and dryer. The pool was completely resurfaced, new jets and new pool pump. Beautiful Travertine floor around the pool and patio area. Large fenced yard with plenty of room for RV and Boat. NO HOA! THIS IS A MUST SEE!
